    </header>
    <div class="body">
      <div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">“We have elected to put our money and faith in a mathematical framework that is free of politics and human error,” Tyler Winklevoss said.</div><br /><br />By stuffing it under your digital mattress?<br /><br />If they're worried about politics and human error, they're looking for a hedge. Gold, for example, will not gain value, but after transaction and storage costs, it won't lose it either.<br /><br />Bitcoins are a perfectly reasonable currency, that is, a device to transfer funds and enable commerce. Like any other currency, it's not an investment.<br /><br />So a handful of idiots are speculating on a billion dollar currency, and they are repeatedly making headlines in a $70 trillion-dollar world economy... why, exactly?
      
    </div>
